Class ViewAppointmentOutcomeBoundary

java.lang.Object
boundary.Boundary
boundary.ViewAppointmentOutcomeBoundary
public class ViewAppointmentOutcomeBoundary extends Boundary
The ViewAppointmentOutcomeBoundary class provides a user interface for viewing appointment outcome records for patients within the Hospital Management System.
